#To [[manipulate]] objects, such as [[ball]]s, [[club]]s, [[beanbag]]s, [[ring]]s, etc. in an [[artful]] or [[artistic]] manner.  Juggling may also include assorted other [[circus]] skills such as the [[diabolo]], [[devil sticks]], [[hat]], and [[cigar]] box manipulation as well.
#:''She can '''juggle''' flaming torches.''
#To [[handle]] or [[manage]] many tasks at once.
#:''He '''juggled''' home, school, and work for two years.''

